(3689, 450, 'banner_content', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Light the fuse on explosive fun with our epic selection of ground fireworks! Get ready to create memories that will spark joy long after the last sparkler fizzles out. Light it up and get ready for some serious backyard BOOM!</p>'),
