(4398, 724, 'banner_content', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Stock your shelves and satisfy your cravings with our Counter Boxes! Buy in bulk for epic savings on fan-favorite fireworks like smoke bombs and tanks. From single purchases to boxfuls of fun, we\'ve got everything you need to keep your fireworks counter crackling with excitement!</p>'),
